<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay20 />這煙火還真是壯觀啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這比我想像中的還要華麗，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人不禁興奮起來了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，煙火爆炸的聲響<delay8 />
還真是大聲啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />連我的體內都感覺到震動啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個綻放於夜空中，<delay20 />發出巨響的花朵好厲害啊！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來不能因為只是煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就小看了它，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨著煙火被接二連三地射向空中，<delay20 />
我的情緒也跟著來到最高潮咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay8 />你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說有面對射向空中的煙火時<delay8 />
所使用的喊聲喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />我是覺得
要喊什麼都可以啦。<delay frames="40" />
像是<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />愛的告白之類的？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇！<delay frames="30" />
剛剛的煙火<delay8 />好大啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />有看到嗎！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惡，<delay20 />這下視線完全無法移開啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有辦法忍住不去廁所<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
直到活動結束為止嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有看到<delay20 />其他傢伙的表情嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家看起來都很高興咧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是也露出了一樣的表情啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這充滿魄力的景象<delay20 />真令人受不了啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay20 />要拍照的話就趁現在！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可別讓按下快門的機會溜走喔！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼啦？<delay20 />是煙火差不多要結束了啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們一起來觀賞最後一發煙火吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也差不多該到活動尾聲了吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能一直像這樣一發接一發地，<delay20 />
不斷發射煙火就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有沒有<delay20 />好好地享受<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的煙火大會啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />你問我有沒有好好享受嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那種事情<delay8 />你不用問，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看我的表情就知道了吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>